T1  - CONSISTENT EXPECTATIONS EQUILIBRIA IN MARKOV REGIME SWITCHING MODELS AND INFLATION DYNAMICS
AU  - Airaudo, Marco
AU  - Hajdini, Ina
Y1  - 2021/11/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12529
