T1  - DISPUTE SETTLEMENT WITH SECOND-ORDER UNCERTAINTY
AU  - Beshkar, Mostafa
AU  - Park, Jee-Hyeong
Y1  - 2021/11/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12519
